[[include :scp-wiki:info:start]]
Rating with info module.
[[include :scp-wiki:info:end]]

+* Info

This is an Amoni-Ram-themed theme, inspired by Amoni-Ram. It is intended to be used for articles featuring/centered around the world of Amoni-Ram, featured in [[[rounderhouse-gold-proposal|]]].

This theme comes with: 
* baked-in [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/theme:extra-black-highlighter-theme dark mode] and [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:toggle-sidebar collapsed sidebar]; 
* elements taken from other themes: [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/theme:space Generic Space Theme], [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/theme:flopstyle-dark Flopstyle DARK], [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/theme:hansarp HANSARP Theme], [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:centered-header-bhl Centered Header BHL] and [https://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/component:motherboard-theme Motherboard Theme of Wanderer's Library];
* wide page on desktop; 
* a big header suited to my tastes.

----

+* Usage

This is a Black Highlighter based theme, meaning you will need to import the Black Highlighter theme as well in order to use this theme. To learn more, go [[[theme:black-highlighter-theme|here]]].

**To import this theme, simply add the following to your page:**

[[div class="blockquote"]]
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]@@
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:fuladh-theme]]@@
[[/div]]

@@ @@

